### ============================================================
### ADMINISTRATION / PERMISSIONS
### ============================================================

### Get Permissions (grouped by module)
GET {{base_api_url}}/administration/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### ============================================================
### ADMINISTRATION / ROLES
### ============================================================

### List Roles
GET {{base_api_url}}/administration/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Create Role
POST {{base_api_url}}/administration/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ochrona",
  "permissions": ["users.view", "cameras.view", "albums.view", "photos.view"]
}

### Update Role
PUT {{base_api_url}}/administration/roles/2
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Monitoring",
  "permissions": ["cameras.view", "cameras.manage", "albums.view", "albums.delete", "photos.view"]
}

### Delete Role
DELETE {{base_api_url}}/administration/roles/4
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
